The paper deals with the task of textual grounding, which involves linking words to objects in images. This task is relevant to computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also uses deep learning techniques, which are commonly used in machine learning (cs.LG) and information retrieval (cs.IR). Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely to be relevant to this paper.
